		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;THE Circumambulation of the Circle of Braja under the lead of Editor is in progress and pure-hearted persons from all parts of the country, irrespective of caste, creed or colour, have availed the opportunity to join the devotional performance which is the consummation of the highest aspirations of the devotee There is no higher function for the soul than the performance of the circumambulation of Sree Brajamandal under the absolute direction of the &lt;i&gt;bona fide&lt;/i&gt; devotee of Krishna.&lt;/p&gt;



